
As a teacher I would like to know if I have class 2 Fridays from now so that I can know if I should assign homework that day.

As a student I would like to know what classes I have on a day far in the future so I can schedule a doctor appointment. 

As a student, I would like to know what classes I have far into the future so I can plan my work ahead and do the correct homework for eaech day.

As a student I would like to know when I have a free period next week so that I can go get Starbucks with my advisor.